ing: 1 small finely chopped green bell pepper
des: "This is a scrum-didley-umptious cheeseball made with cream cheese and dried beef."
ins: In a medium-sized mixing bowl, combine cream cheese, 2/3 of the beef, onion, green bell pepper, Worcestershire sauce, and onion juice. Mix well and shape mixture into a ball. Using the reserved beef, coat the rest of the ball with beef.
